# Title: UAC Bypass Using Event Viewer RecentViews
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-11-22
# Level: high
# Description: Detects the pattern of UAC Bypass using Event Viewer RecentViews
# MITRE Tactic: Privilege Escalation
# Tags: attack.privilege-escalation, attack.stealth
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_uac_bypass_eventvwr_recentviews.yml

CommandLine IN ("*\\Event Viewer\\RecentViews*", "*\\EventV~1\\RecentViews*") CommandLine="*>*"